**BitMinter** is a [[mining pool|Pooled_mining]] operated by Geir Harald Hansen aka [DrHaribo](User:DrHaribo). It launched on 8. July 2011 (1.1).

The [[coinbase]] signature for this pool is: "BitMinter"  (1.2).

Two of its servers are located in the US and one in the EU.

